    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Sometime into the future, in a galaxy much different than ours...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/3b3cdbd3e329d65fe608436b448c8b26.poster.avif?t=1770767921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/3b3cdbd3e329d65fe608436b448c8b26.webm?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/3b3cdbd3e329d65fe608436b448c8b26.mp4?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/fe24c7f674093b407bc8d7927d4fcc50.poster.avif?t=1770767921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/fe24c7f674093b407bc8d7927d4fcc50.webm?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/fe24c7f674093b407bc8d7927d4fcc50.mp4?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Light It Up!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A motely crew of individuals attempt to reverse universal cataclysmic events caused by an organization's network of industries while unearthing a conspiracy against the universe's collective societies. Dive into the world of the SkullStars universe and explore the stories of our cast members.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/f2f79a64ed758d69990e83f8a99235e5.poster.avif?t=1770767921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/f2f79a64ed758d69990e83f8a99235e5.webm?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/f2f79a64ed758d69990e83f8a99235e5.mp4?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/09b7e4ed6a9348dd800f898e4bfc9274.poster.avif?t=1770767921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/09b7e4ed6a9348dd800f898e4bfc9274.webm?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/09b7e4ed6a9348dd800f898e4bfc9274.mp4?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight With Stylish Stars</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;SkullStars: Supernova&quot; is a 2.5D fighter that features stylish graphics that gives 3D models an illustrated design. It features a roster of 12 characters, each with their own unique style that creates a blend of creative play. We’ve got cyborgs, cowboy samurai, space gangs, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/e639c2cea3bf80b37302eb343a9e71c7.poster.avif?t=1770767921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/e639c2cea3bf80b37302eb343a9e71c7.webm?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/e639c2cea3bf80b37302eb343a9e71c7.mp4?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/9913238d4772a9ca77b173c8a697431b.poster.avif?t=1770767921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/9913238d4772a9ca77b173c8a697431b.webm?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/9913238d4772a9ca77b173c8a697431b.mp4?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore our different modes and features!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supernova's mechanics have been designed to allow new players to quickly pick up a character that catches their eye as well as depth to create stunning combos in our various game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the story of your favorite character and discover the lore of the Supernova in our Story Mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight for stardom against friends in our local Versus Mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put your skills of execution to the test with our Challenge Mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharpen your combos or practice moves in our Training Mode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/5179da6a15d63e69d6c63fbc6bbaa91c.poster.avif?t=1770767921\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/5179da6a15d63e69d6c63fbc6bbaa91c.webm?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002580/extras/5179da6a15d63e69d6c63fbc6bbaa91c.mp4?t=1770767921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Banger Music</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jam to the electric soundtrack by the creator, Yair-1 and more talented producers. Land attacks to explosive 808s and futuristic melodies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
